{
  "title": "济州岛游艇攻略 · 预订指南｜Grande Bleu 西归浦帆船（情侣蜜月）",
  "content": "<div style=\"max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;\"><h1 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:2.25rem;color:#0d2645;margin:0 0 1rem;line-height:1.2;font-weight:600;\">济州岛游艇攻略 · 预订指南｜Grande Bleu 西归浦帆船（情侣蜜月）</h1>\n<figure style=\"margin:1rem auto 2.5rem;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/food_0075.jpg\" alt=\"Grande Bleu yacht detail Jeju\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(13,38,69,0.18);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">今日主题</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">这篇文章的主题是 <strong>预订指南</strong>。Grande Bleu 从济州岛西归浦大浦港出发，船型为 catamaran sailing yacht，航程约 1 hour。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">内容主要写给 情侣蜜月，帮助你在预订前快速理解这趟航行适不适合自己。</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/influencer_0229.jpg\" alt=\"Guest enjoying Grande Bleu Jeju yacht\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">航线亮点</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">航行中可以看到 Wolpyeong Jusangjeolli, Wolpyeong Sea Cave, Elephant Rock, and the Daepo coastline 等济州南岸地形。柱状节理从陆地看是一种风景，从海面看则更能感受到高度和岩石纹理。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">这不是半日行程，而是刚好可以放进济州旅行日程中的1小时海上体验。</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/influencer_0074.png\" alt=\"Guest enjoying Grande Bleu Jeju yacht\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">船只与安全</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">Grande Bleu 使用双体帆船。总载客量为 91 guests total: Yacht 550 seats 44 and Yacht 620 seats 47。每次航行都有 licensed captain and engineer onboard，根据天气和海况进行判断。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">如果同行者有儿童、长辈，或担心晕船，双体船的稳定性会是一个重要参考。</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/ocean_0137.jpg\" alt=\"Jeju sailing yacht and coastline\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/food_0241.jpg\" alt=\"Grande Bleu yacht detail Jeju\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">船上包含</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">船上提供 draft beer, wine, Jeju tangerine juice, bottled water, snacks, and cup ramen 等。它不是正式餐厅，而是在看海、拍照、感受海风时轻松享用的配置。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">拍照建议抓住三个时段: 刚出港、靠近海岸线、返航前光线变化的时候。</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/ocean_0168.jpg\" alt=\"Grande Bleu Jeju sunset sailing\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">价格与预订渠道</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">价格参考: Luxury Tour adult ₩60,000 / child ₩40,000, promo ₩48,000 / ₩28,000; Sunset Tour adult ₩70,000 / child ₩40,000, promo ₩56,000 / ₩28,000。实际余位、活动价、改退规则会因平台而不同。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">可通过 Naver, Klook, KKday, and Ctrip/Trip.com partner platforms 等多个合作平台预订。请选择适合自己语言、支付方式和售后规则的平台。</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/ocean_0105.jpg\" alt=\"Grande Bleu Jeju sunset sailing\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">联系方式</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">电话: +82-64-739-7776。Instagram: @gb.jeju。电话主要以韩语沟通，海外旅客建议先查看预订平台页面。</p></div><p style=\"text-align:center;margin:2rem 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.klook.com/en-US/activity/170600-jeju-grandebleu-sunset-yacht-experience/?utm_source=blogger&utm_medium=cta&utm_campaign=jeju_yacht\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#d4a437;color:#fff;padding:1rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;\">今日落日前出航 →</a></p><p style=\"margin-top:2.2rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#777;border-top:1px solid #eee;padding-top:1rem;\"><a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/%E6%B5%8E%E5%B7%9E%E5%B2%9B%E6%B8%B8%E8%89%87\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#济州岛游艇</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/%E6%B5%8E%E5%B7%9E%E5%B2%9B%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#济州岛旅游</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/%E6%B5%8E%E5%B7%9E%E5%B2%9B%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#济州岛攻略</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/Grande%20Bleu\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#GrandeBleu</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%A6%E6%B8%AF\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#大浦港</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/%E5%8F%8C%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%86%E8%88%B9\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#双体帆船</a></p>",
